---
import Analytics from "@vercel/analytics/astro";

const currentYear = new Date().getFullYear();
---

<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="Charizard Token ($CHZ) is a hyper-fast, deflationary crypto asset igniting wealth for its holders."
    />
    <link rel="icon" type="image/png" sizes="32x32" href="/assets/logo.png" />
    <link rel="apple-touch-icon" href="/assets/logo.png" />
    <title>Charizard Token | $CHZ</title>
    <style>
      :root {
        color-scheme: dark;
        --bg-dark: #050309;
        --bg-glow: #140515;
        --bg-accent: radial-gradient(circle at top, rgba(255, 111, 28, 0.32), transparent 58%);
        --brand-fire: #ff7930;
        --brand-dragon: #ff4c20;
        --brand-ember: #ffd166;
        --text-primary: #f7f7ff;
        --text-muted: rgba(247, 247, 255, 0.7);
        --card-bg: rgba(17, 10, 26, 0.68);
        font-family: "Segoe UI", "Inter", "Roboto", system-ui, -apple-system, sans-serif;
      }

      * {
        box-sizing: border-box;
      }

      body {
        margin: 0;
        background: var(--bg-dark);
        color: var(--text-primary);
        line-height: 1.6;
        min-height: 100vh;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        background-image: var(--bg-accent),
          radial-gradient(circle at bottom, rgba(255, 69, 0, 0.14), transparent 60%);
        background-attachment: fixed;
        overflow-x: hidden;
      }

      header {
        padding: 3.5rem 1.5rem 2.5rem;
        text-align: center;
        position: relative;
      }

      header::before {
        content: "";
        position: absolute;
        inset: 10% 12%;
        background: linear-gradient(120deg, rgba(255, 121, 48, 0.18), rgba(56, 17, 71, 0.05));
        filter: blur(80px);
        z-index: -1;
      }

      .logo {
        width: min(320px, 80vw);
        max-width: 280px;
        height: auto;
        margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
        display: block;
        filter: drop-shadow(0 0 1.5rem rgba(255, 90, 0, 0.3));
      }

      h1 {
        font-size: clamp(2.3rem, 5vw, 3.4rem);
        margin: 0.5rem 0;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      p {
        margin: 0.75rem auto;
        max-width: 640px;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .cta {
        margin-top: 1.75rem;
        display: inline-flex;
        gap: 0.85rem;
        justify-content: center;
        align-items: center;
      }

      .cta a {
        padding: 0.85rem 1.7rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        font-weight: 600;
        letter-spacing: 0.02em;
        text-decoration: none;
        transition: transform 120ms ease, box-shadow 120ms ease;
        display: inline-flex;
        align-items: center;
        justify-content: center;
        white-space: nowrap;
      }

      .buy-steps {
        margin: 2.4rem auto 0;
        padding: 1.6rem 1.9rem;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(34, 13, 43, 0.55);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 153, 71, 0.25);
        width: min(560px, 94vw);
        text-align: left;
        box-shadow: 0 1rem 2.4rem rgba(10, 0, 18, 0.35);
      }

      .buy-steps h3 {
        margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: var(--brand-ember);
      }

      .buy-steps p {
        margin: 0.35rem 0;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      .buy-steps code {
        font-family: "JetBrains Mono", "Fira Code", "SFMono-Regular", monospace;
        font-size: 0.95rem;
        color: var(--brand-ember);
        background: rgba(255, 121, 48, 0.1);
        padding: 0.2rem 0.4rem;
        border-radius: 8px;
        display: block;
        word-break: break-all;
        overflow-wrap: anywhere;
      }

      @media (max-width: 900px) {
        header {
          padding: 3.1rem 1.3rem 2.3rem;
        }

        main {
          padding: 2.3rem 1.3rem 3.6rem;
        }

        section {
          padding: 2rem 1.6rem;
        }

        .buy-steps {
          padding: 1.5rem 1.7rem;
        }
      }

      .cta-primary {
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-fire), var(--brand-dragon));
        color: #100307;
        box-shadow: 0 0.7rem 2rem rgba(255, 98, 0, 0.35);
      }

      .cta-primary:hover {
        transform: translateY(-2px);
        box-shadow: 0 1.1rem 2.6rem rgba(255, 111, 0, 0.38);
      }

      .cta-secondary {
        color: var(--brand-ember);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 191, 112, 0.4);
        background: rgba(37, 15, 42, 0.35);
      }

      main {
        display: grid;
        gap: 3rem;
        padding: 2.5rem 1.5rem 4rem;
        max-width: 1040px;
        width: 100%;
        margin: 0 auto;
        flex: 1;
      }

      section {
        background: var(--card-bg);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 153, 71, 0.18);
        border-radius: 22px;
        padding: 2.2rem 1.8rem;
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
        box-shadow: 0 1.4rem 3.4rem rgba(7, 0, 12, 0.4);
      }

      section h2 {
        font-size: clamp(1.6rem, 3.2vw, 2.2rem);
        margin: 0 0 1rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
      }

      .stat-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.4rem;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
        margin-top: 1.6rem;
      }

      .stat {
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(23, 7, 32, 0.55);
        padding: 1.4rem 1.2rem;
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 121, 48, 0.2);
      }

      .stat span:first-child {
        display: block;
        font-size: 0.9rem;
        letter-spacing: 0.04em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
        color: rgba(255, 209, 102, 0.78);
      }

      .stat strong {
        display: block;
        font-size: 1.6rem;
        margin-top: 0.35rem;
        color: var(--text-primary);
      }

      ul {
        list-style: none;
        padding: 0;
        margin: 1.5rem 0 0;
        display: grid;
        gap: 0.9rem;
      }

      li {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: auto 1fr;
        align-items: baseline;
        gap: 0.65rem;
        color: var(--text-muted);
      }

      li::before {
        content: "";
        width: 0.55rem;
        height: 0.55rem;
        border-radius: 999px;
        background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--brand-ember), var(--brand-fire));
        box-shadow: 0 0 0.6rem rgba(255, 138, 41, 0.7);
        margin-top: 0.3rem;
      }

      .roadmap-grid {
        display: grid;
        gap: 1.5rem;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(240px, 1fr));
        margin-top: 1.6rem;
      }

      .roadmap-card {
        padding: 1.4rem 1.2rem;
        border-radius: 18px;
        background: rgba(31, 9, 41, 0.55);
        border: 1px solid rgba(255, 111, 48, 0.18);
      }

      .roadmap-card h3 {
        margin: 0 0 0.6rem;
        font-size: 1.1rem;
        color: var(--brand-ember);
        letter-spacing: 0.03em;
        text-transform: uppercase;
      }

      footer {
        padding: 1.8rem 1.5rem 3rem;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 0.85rem;
        color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.55);
      }

      footer a {
        color: var(--brand-ember);
        text-decoration: none;
      }

      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        header {
          padding-top: 2.8rem;
        }

        .cta {
          flex-direction: column;
          width: min(320px, 100%);
          margin-left: auto;
          margin-right: auto;
        }

        section {
          padding: 1.8rem 1.4rem;
        }

        .buy-steps {
          width: 100%;
          padding: 1.4rem 1.3rem;
        }

        .buy-steps code {
          font-size: 0.88rem;
          word-break: break-word;
          overflow-wrap: anywhere;
        }

        .buy-steps p {
          margin: 0.45rem 0;
        }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <header>
      <img
        src="/assets/logo.png"
        alt="Charizard Token emblem"
        class="logo"
        width="520"
        loading="eager"
      />
      <h1>Charizard Token // $CHZ</h1>
      <p>
        Forged in digital fire, Charizard Token is a 1,000,000,000 supply, ultra-fast deflationary asset engineered to empower a fearless community.
        Every burn fuels scarcity, every holder becomes part of the flame.
      </p>
      <div class="cta">
        <a class="cta-primary" href="#tokenomics">Explore Tokenomics</a>
        <a class="cta-secondary" href="#ignite">Join the Flame</a>
      </div>
      <div class="buy-steps">
        <h3>Steps to Buy</h3>
        <p>Transfer SOL to <code>9Vsan6w7QaGHDEbF1JcgruDVcbsS3xkEMgeZmAQGJ5wP</code></p>
        <p><strong>0.1 SOL = 350,000 $CHZ</strong></p>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main>
      <section id="tokenomics">
        <h2>Dragon-Forged Tokenomics</h2>
        <p>
          $CHZ blends iconic Charizard energy with disciplined supply mechanics to ignite growth while protecting holders from runaway inflation.
        </p>
        <div class="stat-grid">
          <div class="stat">
            <span>Total Supply</span>
            <strong>1,000,000,000 $CHZ</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span>Burn Mechanism</span>
            <strong>Auto Deflationary</strong>
          </div>
          <div class="stat">
            <span>Liquidity</span>
            <strong>Battle-Tested Pools</strong>
          </div>
        </div>
        <ul>
          <li>Dynamic burn events reduce circulating supply with every major milestone.</li>
          <li>Community vaults fund cross-chain expansion and real-world utility.</li>
          <li>Transparent on-chain governance lets flame-bearers vote on the next evolution.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="utility">
        <h2>Utility that Breathes Fire</h2>
        <p>
          Charizard Token is more than a meme—it is a wealth-engine built for blazing-fast transactions, gamified rewards, and collaborative quests that keep the ecosystem thriving.
        </p>
        <ul>
          <li>Flash-speed transfers optimized for low fees, even when the market heats up.</li>
          <li>Earn ember rewards by staking $CHZ during community burn campaigns.</li>
          <li>Unlock exclusive drops, merch, and metaverse arenas with your token holdings.</li>
        </ul>
      </section>

      <section id="ignite">
        <h2>Ignition Roadmap</h2>
        <p>
          The evolution of $CHZ stays true to the Charizard spirit—strategic, unstoppable, and ready to conquer the next arena.
        </p>
        <div class="roadmap-grid">
          <div class="roadmap-card">
            <h3>Phase 01 // Spark</h3>
            <p>Token launch, genesis airdrop to early flame-bearers, liquidity ignition, and the first ceremonial burn to mark the founding flame.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="roadmap-card">
            <h3>Phase 02 // Blaze</h3>
            <p>Cross-exchange listings, GameFi integrations, and Charizard lore-driven NFT ascent.</p>
          </div>
          <div class="roadmap-card">
            <h3>Phase 03 // Inferno</h3>
            <p>DAO governance, recurring deflation events, and global community raids to expand the fire.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="community">
        <h2>Empower the Holders</h2>
        <p>
          Every token holder is part of an elite squadron of fire-breathers. Together we strike, we burn supply, and we push $CHZ to new heights.
          Join the mission to transform early believers into the next wave of crypto millionaires.
        </p>
        <div class="cta">
          <a class="cta-primary" href="#">Get $CHZ</a>
          <a class="cta-secondary" href="/litepaper" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">View Litepaper</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <p>
        {currentYear} Charizard Token. Fan-made homage inspired by the legend of Charizard.<br />
        Always DYOR. Crypto assets carry risk.
      </p>
    </footer>

    <Analytics />
  </body>
</html>
